<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-15 15:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5530 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBO-ARATON-COLUMN-NYT     08-15 0940
