<SLUG> BC-NY-CHEFS-FILM-400&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CINEMATIC TRUTH FOR YOUNG CHEFS 
</HEADLINE>
  (Also moved in ``e'' category.) 
(js) 
 BY CLAUDIA ROWE   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   HYDE PARK, N.Y. _ At the Culinary Institute of America, where
