<P>
   EMBASSY _ NAIROBI _ A look at how the U.S. embassy is faring in
Nairobi since the bombing. Where is it operating? Color scene
piece. (Melvin, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   For release Sunday, Aug. 16.
